          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Psychic Power" typeId="9060-973c-99e9-75b4">After this unit makes a Psychic Test, if that Psychic Test had two or more dice with the same result, this unit suffers D3 SW, the nearest visible enemy unit with 24” suffers 2D3 SW and this unit gains Psyker 3. Then, this unit may make a Psychic Test.</characteristic>
