            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">While selecting targets for this unit&apos;s Bombast Field Gun or Malleaus Rocket Launcher, if you have no ready units except units with Artillery Support, you may ‘call for an artillery strike’. If you do, you may instead target an enemy unit within 16&quot; of and visible to any of your infantry units within 16&quot; of this unit. Additionally, for each attack made for that weapon this turn, add 1 to the Hit Roll of that attack.</characteristic>
