    <profile name="Recrew" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="9567-753f-2da2-e85a">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After one of your friendly infantry units finishes a March within 1” of this unit, you may remove up to 10 models from that unit. If you do, this unit Heals 1 for each model removed.</characteristic>
